		Jan 17, 2011, 11:37AM	</div>
	
	
  	
  		<h1><a href="http://www.splicetoday.com/pop-culture/all-the-young-mods">All the Young Mods</a></h1>
  	
  	
  	
  		<div class="byline">
  			<a href="http://www.splicetoday.com/author/Russ%20Smith">Russ Smith</a>
  		</div>
  	
  	
	
	
	
  	  
    	
    	  
    	    <div id="topper-image" class="clearfix">
    	     <img alt="Picture_3_large" src="/vault/posts/0002/1408/Picture_3_large.png?1295282240" />
    	    </div>
    	  
    	
	
	
	
		<p class="caption"><p><a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/brizzlebornandbred/" target="_blank">brizzle born and bred</a></p></p>
	
	
	
